      "description": "This 2017 Lexus RX 350 in Nebula Gray Pearl offers a perfect balance of luxury and dependability. The exterior maintains a high-gloss finish, with only minor stone chips on the front bumper consistent with light highway use. Inside, the Parchment leather upholstery is clean and supple, showing very minimal wear on the driver\u2019s side bolster and no interior odors. Every feature, including the panoramic sunroof, navigation system, and dual-zone climate control, operates exactly as intended. Mechanically, the car is in excellent health; it has been dealer-serviced on schedule, with a smooth-shifting transmission and a quiet, responsive V6 engine. The tires are matching Michelins with plenty of life left, and the brake pads were recently replaced. It comes complete with two key fobs, all-weather floor mats, and a documented maintenance log. This is a solid, honest vehicle ready for its next long-term owner.",
